OL,7,FThe Scot was forthright in his
OL,8,Frejection of Reform UK, which has
OL,9,Fsurged in the polls since the Brexiter
OL,10,Ftook over two weeks ago, telling ITV
OL,11,FNews people must take Farage's self-
