OL,12,Fachieve his party's purpose of gaining
OL,13,Findependence from the UK, the Scottish
OL,14,FNational Party needs to stage a
OL,15,Fcomeback to reverse the polls.
OL,17,FOne step toward that, Flynn will hope,
OL,18,Fwas an interview with ITV News where
