OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,FFlynn admitted to ITV News that
OL,8,FScotland has a "problem with
OL,9,Fmigration", but it was not the same
OL,10,Fissue raised by Nigel Farage, Rishi
OL,11,FSunak and Sir Keir Starmer; that it's
OL,12,Ftoo high.
OL,14,F"Our problem with migration is we
OL,15,Fdon't have enough. We need more people
OL,16,Fcoming to live and work in Scotland,"
OL,17,Fhe said, pointing to staff shortages
OL,18,Fin the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
