OL,7,FBut migrants aren't only needed to
OL,8,Ffill critical vacancies, Flynn added,
OL,9,Fthey "boost the wider economy" by
OL,10,Fpaying taxes and spending money.
OL,12,F"This is where politicians need to
OL,13,Fdeal in facts rather than right-wing
OL,14,Fpopulist rhetoric," he said, in
OL,15,Freference to Farage.
OL,17,F"Unfortunately, far too many
OL,18,Fpoliticians are scared to do that"
OL,19,Fbecause they are "scared of Nigel
OL,20,FFarage".
