OL,7,F"And I think it's right that we
OL,8,Fscrutinise their proposals now, as
OL,9,FI've sought to do over the course of
OL,10,Frecent weeks and months."
OL,12,FFlynn has repeatedly condemned
OL,13,FLabour's position on Gaza, calling for
OL,14,Fan end to the weapons trade with
OL,15,FIsrael, an issue he said he will
OL,16,Fcontinue to raise.
OL,18,FHe also said Labour must also be "held
OL,19,Fto account" on issues including child
OL,20,Fpoverty and developing a closer
OL,21,Frelationship with Europe after Brexit.
