OL,7,FAsked about the possibility of a Prime
OL,8,FMinister Farage, Flynn said he could
OL,9,Frespond with a flippant answer "but I
OL,10,Fthink it's probably moved beyond that
OL,11,Fnow. I think we do have to take this
OL,12,Fvery seriously now."
