OL,7,FLike most parties other than Labour
OL,8,Fand the Conservatives, who massively
OL,9,Fbenefit from the First Past the Post
OL,10,F(FPP) voting system, the SNP wants to
OL,11,Freplace it with proportional
OL,12,Frepresentation.
OL,14,FThe main criticism of FPP is that the
OL,15,Fnumber of votes for a party does not
OL,16,Ftranslate into an equivalent number of
OL,17,Fseats because only the winner in each
OL,18,Fconstituency gets representation.
