OL,7,FSo a party could get millions of votes
OL,8,Fby finishing second in areas across
OL,9,Fthe country but get no seats in
OL,10,FParliament.
OL,12,FThe SNP has had great success under
OL,13,FFirst Past the Post, winning several
OL,14,Fdozen seats in every General Election
OL,15,Fsince 2015.
OL,17,FBut Flynn said: "Sometimes in politics
OL,18,Fit's about doing the right thing -
OL,19,Fgetting rid of First Past the Post
OL,20,Fwould be doing the right thing".
