OL,7,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,8,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,9,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,10,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,12,FIs independence still an SNP priority?
OL,14,FThe SNP's sole goal when it was set up
OL,15,Fwas to campaign for an independent
OL,16,FScotland. The party came very close
OL,17,Fwhen it forced a referendum in 2014,
OL,18,Fbut lost with 55% of voters rejecting
OL,19,Fit.
