OL,4,CSNP's Stephen Flynn answers your
OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,FBut the 2015 general election proved
OL,8,Fthe dream was not dead. The party got
OL,9,Fmore votes than it ever had, winning a
OL,10,Fhuge 56 seats, up from the six it
OL,11,Fpreviously held.
OL,13,FSince then, however, leaders in
OL,14,FWestminster have repeatedly rejected
OL,15,Fthe idea of another referendum on
OL,16,Findependence.
OL,18,FAnd with the party engulfed by scandal
OL,19,Fsince the departure of Nicola
OL,20,FSturgeon, independence any time soon
OL,21,Ffeels unrealistic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
