OL,3,C'I'm not scared of Nigel Farage':
OL,4,CSNP's Stephen Flynn answers your
OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,FFlynn does not think so.
OL,9,F"I would like to think that we could
OL,10,Fget independence referendum within the
OL,11,Fnext five years," he said, "but
OL,12,Fultimately, that's for the people of
OL,13,FScotland to decide.
OL,15,F"A vote for the SNP is a vote for
OL,16,Findependence. It's who we are.
OL,18,F"We believe that Scotland's future
OL,19,Fshould be in Scotland's hands, and the
OL,20,Fonly way to make that happen is for
OL,21,Fthe people of Scotland to vote for it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/21
